uck you into bed each night?\")</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Nope, Mama\'s a grown-up girl now, so she only gets to see her Mama when she visits Yammo\'s house.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> That make me so sad.\r\n\r\n<em>So now, it makes me kind of sad too...</em>','Growing up is hard to do.','','publish','open','open','','drake-in-the-car-2','','','2014-06-11 04:04:02','2014-06-11 04:04:02','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=168',0,'post','',0),(169,1,'2014-06-10 16:54:34','2014-06-10 16:54:34','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mama, it make me so happy that we go to see Yammo (grandma).\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> It makes me happy, too, Buddy.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yammo is you Mama?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Yep.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> She come make you sleep at night? (basically, does she come tuck you into bed each night)\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Nope, Mama\'s a grown-up girl now, so she only gets to see her Mama when she visits Yammo\'s house.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> That make me so sad.\r\n<em>So now, it makes me kind of sad too...</em>','Drake, in the car','','inherit','open','open','','168-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 16:54:34','2014-06-10 16:54:34','',168,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=169',0,'revision','',0),(170,1,'2012-02-16 16:55:20','2012-02-16 16:55:20','<strong>Drake:</strong> \"Dada?\"\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> \"Yep, Buddy, that\'s Dada marrying Mama.\"\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> \"Love love?\"\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> \"Yes, Mama and Dada love each other SOO much! And we love YOU so much, Drake.\"\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>walking away and nodding</em>:</strong> \"Love yeah! Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!\"','Drake, pointing to a wedding photo on our wall','','publish','open','open','','drake-pointing-to-a-wedding-photo-on-our-wall','','','2014-06-11 04:04:40','2014-06-11 04:04:40','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=170',0,'post','',0),(171,1,'2014-06-10 16:57:01','2014-06-10 16:57:01','<strong>Drake:</strong> \"Dada?\"\r\n<strong