wn!','','publish','open','open','','drake-brings-me-the-remote','','','2014-06-11 04:06:29','2014-06-11 04:06:29','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=174',0,'post','',0),(175,1,'2014-06-10 16:59:47','2014-06-10 16:59:47','<strong>Me:</strong> You want to watch some Sesame Street, kiddo?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Shakes head.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Movie?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Shakes head.\r\n<strong>Me, <em>after remembering his enthusiasm for sports</em>:</strong> football?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Ball! Ball!\r\n<em>I turns on college football</em>\r\n<strong>Drake: </strong>laughter, raises arms to make the sign for touchdown.','Drake, brings me the remote','','inherit','open','open','','174-revision-v1','','','2014-06-10 16:59:47','2014-06-10 16:59:47','',174,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=175',0,'revision','',0),(176,1,'2011-12-13 16:59:57','2011-12-13 16:59:57','<strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you getting sleepy?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>emphatic nodding</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Ok, let\'s do nappy time!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>grabs blanket, marches to bedroom, points at crib.</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> No more snuggles, just bed?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>More nodding.</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Ok, love you buddy. (kissed him, put him in crib)\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>waves bye bye, lays down.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Easiest nap time EVER.</em>','Naptime','','publish','open','open','','drake-before-nap','','','2014-06-11 04:07:38','2014-06-11 04:07:38','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.dev:8888/?p=176',0,'post','',0),(177,1,'2014-06-10 17:01:08','2014-06-10 17:01:08','<strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you getting sleepy?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> emphatic nodding\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Ok, let\'s do nappy time!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> grabs blanket, marches to bedroom, points at crib.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> No more snuggles, just bed?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> More nodding.\r\n<strong>Me:</stro