!!! <em>(does a little dance)</em> Wait! Will I have to put on pants when she gets here?\r\n<strong>Me</strong>: What do you think? Should you?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: Well, I supposed to wear pants when girls come over. So maybe. But Destiny is not a GIRL! She\'s an AUNT! So it\'s cool, I\'ll just be naked.','Drake, on the dress code at our house','','inherit','open','open','','41-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:19:08','2014-06-11 03:19:08','',41,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/41-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(239,1,'2014-06-11 03:20:22','2014-06-11 03:20:22','<strong>Adrian</strong>,<strong> <em>after reading bedtime stories</em></strong>: Ok, can I cuddle you for a while, since Mommy got to give you a bath?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: No. Mommy always does the cuddle.\r\n<strong>Adrian</strong>: But can I do it instead, just tonight?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: Daddy, that\'s ridiculous.','Bedtime cuddles','','inherit','open','open','','44-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:20:22','2014-06-11 03:20:22','',44,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/44-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(240,1,'2014-06-11 03:21:20','2014-06-11 03:21:20','<em>He said this completely out of the blue.</em>\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: When I was Santa Clause, I had a white beard and a mustache, and cars in my pockets, and I gives presents and I was really strong. Ho, Ho, Ho!!','A Statement by Drake','','inherit','open','open','','46-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:21:20','2014-06-11 03:21:20','',46,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/46-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(241,1,'2014-06-11 03:22:29','2014-06-11 03:22:29','<strong>Me</strong>: What does the fox say?\n<strong>Drake</strong>: Ring dingy ding dingy ding! And wa papapapapa POW!\n<strong>Me</strong>: Is that what they really say? Drake: no, just in Daddy\'s video. Real foxes is nice and quiet.\n<strong>Me</strong>: What do you think the fox would say about that crazy video?\n<strong>Drake</strong>: It would hurt his feelings because real foxes not silly. They are nice. And quiet. And they don\'t chase mousies. So don\'t show foxes that video, Mom. I\'m going to hold off on telling him the truth about foxes and their relationship with mousies.','Again about foxes','','inherit','open','open','','48-autosave-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:22:29','2014-06-11 03:22:29','',48,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/48-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(242,1,'2014-06-11 03:23:07','2014-06-11 03:23:07','<strong>Me</strong>: What does the fox say?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: Ring dingy ding dingy ding! And wa papapapapa POW!\r\n<strong>Me</strong>: Is that what they really say? Drake: no, just in Daddy\'s video. Real foxes is nice and quiet.\r\n<strong>Me</strong>: What do you think the fox would say about that crazy video?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>: It would hurt his feelings because real foxes not silly. They are nice. And quiet. And they don\'t chase mousies. So don\'t show foxes that video, Mom.\r\n\r\n<em>(I\'m going to hold off on telling him the truth about foxes and their relationship with mousies.)</em>','Again about foxes','','inherit','open','open','','48-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:23:07','2014-06-11 03:23:07','',48,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/48-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(243,1,'2014-06-11 03:24:13','2014-06-11 03:24:13','<strong>Me</strong>: Hey Drake, want to help me wrap these presents?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>,<strong> <em>sighing deeply</em></strong>: I wish I could... but my monster trucks are all JACKED UP, thanks to my BLASTED DADDY!!!','Drake using his Dad\'s favorite expression','','inherit','open','open','','50-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:24:13','2014-06-11 03:24:13','',50,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/50-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(244,1,'2014-06-11 03:24:41','2014-06-11 03:24:41','<strong>Me</strong>: Hey Drake, want to help me wrap these presents?\r\n<strong>Drake</strong>,<str