4-06-11 03:56:49','2014-06-11 03:56:49','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, there\'s something on me!\r\n<strong>Me, <em>concerned</em>:</strong> what is it, Buddy? Are you ok?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> There\'s something on me. Want to see?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Show me. What\'s on you?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>(Turns around, pulls down Lightning McQueen underwear, and giggles.)</em> It\'s a BUTT!!\r\n\r\n<em>I demand to know who taught him that.</em>','Drake, with a hand on his rear end, as if he is hurt','','inherit','open','open','','139-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:56:49','2014-06-11 03:56:49','',139,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/139-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(289,1,'2014-06-11 03:57:25','2014-06-11 03:57:25','<strong>Drake:</strong> Play with me, Daisy!\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Drake, our Daisy is not feeling very well today. She just wants to be still because she had surgery yesterday.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Wanna cuddle, Daisy? OK! <em>(Pets her softly, lays down next to her.)</em> you is so pretty, Daisy. I like you haircut. Sorry you got surgeried.','Drake and Miss Daisy','','inherit','open','open','','141-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:57:25','2014-06-11 03:57:25','',141,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/141-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(290,1,'2014-06-11 03:57:58','2014-06-11 03:57:58','<strong>Me:</strong> Okay, Drake, time for a haircut!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> No, that\'s not fun and I don\'t like haircuts because I\'m big and strong today.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> You could still be big and strong with a haircut.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Nope. I\'ll just be little.','Who told him the story of Samson??','','inherit','open','open','','147-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:57:58','2014-06-11 03:57:58','',147,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/147-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(291,1,'2014-06-11 03:58:29','2014-06-11 03:58:29','<strong>Adrian:</strong> what are you doing, Drake?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> I\'m looking for my motorcycle.<em> (Starts looking)</em> Motorcycle? Motorcycle?\r\n<em>(Looks at Adrian and pauses.)</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Daddy, did you eat my motorcycle?','Daddy ate it.','','inherit','open','open','','145-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:58:29','2014-06-11 03:58:29','',145,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/145-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(292,1,'2014-06-11 03:59:27','2014-06-11 03:59:27','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mama, did you grow these crunchies in you garden?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> No, buddy. Mama bought them at the store.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Is them veggie-bells <em>(Vegetables)</em>?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Nope. We are making a treat.\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>patting my leg</em>:</strong> Ok. I won\'t tell Yammo.','Drake, as we make Rice Krispie treats together','','inherit','open','open','','149-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:59:27','2014-06-11 03:59:27','',149,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/149-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(293,1,'2014-06-11 03:59:55','2014-06-11 03:59:55','\"I pretty handsome.\" \"I always trying to be good.\" \"I such a big good SWIMMER!\" \"I can play drums nice and LOUD.\" \"I a smart boy, Mommy!\" \"I love Mommy and Daddy and them loves me, too!\" \"Yammo is missing me because she is on the boat far away.\" \"I is a fast racer.\" \"I will grow up big and strong.\" \"I can do it because I Drake.\"\r\n\r\n<em>LOVE his crazy confidence. LOVE.</em>','A few things Drake has said about himself today','','inherit','open','open','','151-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 03:59:55','2014-06-11 03:59:55','',151,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/151-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(294,1,'2014-06-11 04:00:29','2014-06-11 04:00:29','<strong>Drake:</strong> Daddy, can I watch monster trucks on you phone?\r\n<strong>Adrian:</strong> No.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> PLEASE???\r\n<strong>Adrian:</strong> Read my lips. NO! <em>(tickles Drake)</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>(giggling)</em> Read MY lips! YES!','Drake, on watching monster trucks on Adrian\'s phone','','inherit','open','open','','153-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:00:29','2014-06-11 04:00:29','',153,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/153-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(295,1,'2014-06-11 04:01:12','2014-06-11 04:01:12','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy! I have a present for you! <em>(He hands me a spray bottle of all-purpose cleaner.)</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Thanks, dude.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> It\'s cleaning stuffs. Because you is always cleaning and cleaning and CLEANING!\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Why do you think I do all that cleaning, my dear?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Because you LOVE IT SO MUCH!','A present from Drake','','inherit','open','open','','155-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:01:12','2014-06-11 04:01:12','',155,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/155-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(296,1,'2014-06-11 04:01:59','2014-06-11 04:01:59','<strong>Me:</strong> Drake, stop picking your nose, please.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> I\'m not picking my nose.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Really?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Nope. I\'m just picking my BOOGERS, not my NOSE!\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Why are you doing that?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> They <em>(the boogers)</em> don\'t like it in there, it\'s TOO CROWDED!','He\'s on a roll','','inherit','open','open','','159-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:01:59','2014-06-11 04:01:59','',159,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/159-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(297,1,'2014-06-11 04:02:53','2014-06-11 04:02:53','<strong>Drake,<em> while slipping my shoe on my foot for me</em>:</strong> \"Mommy, you is a princess.\"\r\n<strong>Mommy:</strong> <em>(Speechless.)</em>','Prince Drake','','inherit','open','open','','165-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:02:53','2014-06-11 04:02:53','',165,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/165-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(298,1,'2014-06-11 04:04:02','2014-06-11 04:04:02','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mama, it make me so happy that we go to see Yammo\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> It makes me happy, too, Buddy.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yammo is you Mama?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Yep.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> She come make you sleep at night?<em> (Basically, \"does she come tuck you into bed each night?\")</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Nope, Mama\'s a grown-up girl now, so she only gets to see her Mama when she visits Yammo\'s house.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> That make me so sad.\r\n\r\n<em>So now, it makes me kind of sad too...</em>','Growing up is hard to do.','','inherit','open','open','','168-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:04:02','2014-06-11 04:04:02','',168,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/168-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(299,1,'2014-06-11 04:04:40','2014-06-11 04:04:40','<strong>Drake:</strong> \"Dada?\"\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> \"Yep, Buddy, that\'s Dada marrying Mama.\"\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> \"Love love?\"\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> \"Yes, Mama and Dada love each other SOO much! And we love YOU so much, Drake.\"\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>walking away and nodding</em>:</strong> \"Love yeah! Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!\"','Drake, pointing to a wedding photo on our wall','','inherit','open','open','','170-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:04:40','2014-06-11 04:04:40','',170,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/170-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(300,1,'2014-06-11 04:05:31','2014-06-11 04:05:31','<strong>Me,<em> half-singing</em>:</strong> Drake, can you tell me how to get, how to get to Sesame Street?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>Nods seriously, takes me by the hand, walks me to the living room, points to the television.</em>','Drake, on Sesame Street','','inherit','open','open','','172-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:05:31','2014-06-11 04:05:31','',172,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/172-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(301,1,'2014-06-11 04:06:29','2014-06-11 04:06:29','<strong>Me:</strong> You want to watch some Sesame Street, kiddo?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>Shakes head.</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Movie?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong><em> Shakes head.</em>\r\n<strong>Me, <em>after remembering his enthusiasm for sports</em>:</strong> Football?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Ball! Ball!\r\n<em>I turn on college football</em>\r\n<strong>Drake: </strong><em>Laughs, raises arms to make the sign for touchdown.</em>','Touchdown!','','inherit','open','open','','174-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:06:29','2014-06-11 04:06:29','',174,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/174-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(302,1,'2014-06-11 04:07:38','2014-06-11 04:07:38','<strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you getting sleepy?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>emphatic nodding</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Ok, let\'s do nappy time!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>grabs blanket, marches to bedroom, points at crib.</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> No more snuggles, just bed?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>More nodding.</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Ok, love you buddy. (kissed him, put him in crib)\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> <em>waves bye bye, lays down.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>Easiest nap time EVER.</em>','Naptime','','inherit','open','open','','176-revision-v1','','','2014-06-11 04:07:38','2014-06-11 04:07:38','',176,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/11/176-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(304,1,'2014-06-14 19:27:39','2014-06-14 19:27:39','<span class=\"userContent\" style=\"color: #37404e;\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;K&quot;}\"><em>Conversation with Drake and Cousin Tacy (who is also three years old)</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Crawl under me like a tunnel, Tacy!\r\n<strong>Tacy:</strong> I\'ll roll. (Tacy rolls, but is far too large to roll under Drake.)\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Tacy, you don\'t fit!\r\n<strong>Tacy:</strong> I roll! (Tries again, still unsuccessful.)\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>giggling</em>:</strong> Tacy! Tacy! You don\'t fit! You are a crazy little chicken nugget!\r\n<strong>Tacy, <em>also giggling:</em></strong> Yeah! Crazy!</span><span class=\"userContentSecondary fcg\" style=\"color: gray;\"> </span>','Crazy Chicken Nugget','','publish','open','open','','crazy-chicken-nugget','','','2014-06-14 19:27:39','2014-06-14 19:27:39','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=304',0,'post','',0),(305,1,'2014-06-14 19:27:39','2014-06-14 19:27:39','<span class=\"userContent\" style=\"color: #37404e;\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;K&quot;}\"><em>Conversation with Drake and Cousin Tacy (who is also three years old)</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Crawl under me like a tunnel, Tacy!\r\n<strong>Tacy:</strong> I\'ll roll. (Tacy rolls, but is far too large to roll under Drake.)\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Tacy, you don\'t fit!\r\n<strong>Tacy:</strong> I roll! (Tries again, still unsuccessful.)\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>giggling</em>:</strong> Tacy! Tacy! You don\'t fit! You are a crazy little chicken nugget!\r\n<strong>Tacy, <em>also giggling:</em></strong> Yeah! Crazy!</span><span class=\"userContentSecondary fcg\" style=\"color: gray;\"> </span>','Crazy Chicken Nugget','','inherit','open','open','','304-revision-v1','','','2014-06-14 19:27:39','2014-06-14 19:27:39','',304,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/14/304-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(307,1,'2014-06-18 03:01:58','2014-06-18 03:01:58','<span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> ok, Drake, time to go potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> I already went potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> You did? When?</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Um, the other day...</span>','Time to go potty','','publish','open','open','','time-to-go-potty','','','2014-06-18 03:01:58','2014-06-18 03:01:58','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.