ationswithdrake.com/2014/06/18/309-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(311,1,'2014-06-18 03:03:38','2014-06-18 03:03:38','<strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, just turn on my Avengers <em>(cartoon version)</em>!\r\n<span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Sorry, babe, I can\'t get it to work.</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> This kind of thing wouldn\'t happen if Daddy were here right now.</span>','Father\'s Day Conversation with Drake, while I struggled to make Netflix work','','inherit','open','open','','309-revision-v1','','','2014-06-18 03:03:38','2014-06-18 03:03:38','',309,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/18/309-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(312,1,'2014-06-18 03:06:14','2014-06-18 03:06:14','<span style=\"color: #37404e;\">The child formerly known as \"Drake\" no longer wishes to answer to that name. Hereafter, he prefers to be known as \"Captain America.\" \"Cap\" is also acceptable.\r\nThank you, that is all.</span>','Public Service Announcement','','publish','open','open','','public-service-announcement','','','2014-06-18 03:06:14','2014-06-18 03:06:14','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=312',0,'post','',0),(313,1,'2014-06-18 03:04:54','2014-06-18 03:04:54','<span style=\"color: #37404e;\">The child formerly known as \"Drake\" no longer wishes to answer to that name. Hereafter, he prefers to be known as \"Captain America.\" \"Cap\" is also acceptable.\r\nThank you, that is all.</span>','Public Service Announcement','','inherit','open','open','','312-revision-v1','','','2014-06-18 03:04:54','2014-06-18 03:04:54','',312,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/06/18/312-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(314,1,'2014-06-18 03:06:01','2014-06-18 03:06:01','<strong>Drake, holding up a Hotwheels car:</strong> Mommy, this car is rich!\r\n<span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Dude, what does \"rich\" mean?</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #3