ng> We can make it a quick bath if you want. But you need to get clean, Buddy.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Ok. Just as long as I\'m not TOO clean...\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s526x395/10636128_10100234240397246_5374426274901486898_n.jpg?oh=02a765b1f67790746265a2bfa15afbc4&amp;oe=54902EF9&amp;__gda__=1419156034_76dbd358ccd4042b600e2b8028c923cf\" alt=\"Pruney toed Drake\" width=\"395\" height=\"395\" />','Conversation with pruny-toes Drake','','inherit','open','open','','348-revision-v1','','','2014-09-10 13:05:52','2014-09-10 20:05:52','',348,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/09/10/348-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(350,1,'2014-08-30 13:07:37','2014-08-30 20:07:37','<br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake, while Hannah changes baby Henry\'s diaper:</strong> Nana Hookum, Henry pooped in his diaper A LOT!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Hannah:</strong> Yep, but I\'m cleaning him up!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake, <em>sounding betrayed:</em></strong> But I told him NOT to poop in his diap\' and to ONLY poop in the potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Hannah:</strong> I\'m sure he wants to, Bud, but he can\'t even sit up yet. How can he poop on the potty?</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">**Drake thinks about it, then holds out his arms to take the baby.**</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Give him to me! I will hold him over the potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">Parenting disclosure: I\'m sure Hannah would like it known that she refused Drake\'s offer to help and continued dealing with Henry\'s diaper the traditional way.</span></em>','(Another) Conversation with Drake, this time with Aunt Hannah','','publish','open','open','','another-conversation-with-drake-this-time-with-aunt-hannah','','','2014-09-10 13:07:57','2014-09-10 20:07:57','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=350',0,'post','',0),(351,1,'2014-09-10 13:07:37','2014-09-10 20:07:37','<br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake, while Hannah changes baby Henry\'s diaper:</strong> Nana Hookum, Henry pooped in his diaper A LOT!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Hannah:</strong> Yep, but I\'m cleaning him up!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake, <em>sounding betrayed:</em></strong> But I told him NOT to poop in his diap\' and to ONLY poop in the potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Hannah:</strong> I\'m sure he wants to, Bud, but he can\'t even sit up yet. How can he poop on the potty?</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">**Drake thinks about it, then holds out his arms to take the baby.**</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Give him to me! I will hold him over the potty!</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">Parenting disclosure: I\'m sure Hannah would like it known that she refused Drake\'s offer to help and continued dealing with Henry\'s diaper the traditional way.</span></em>','(Another) Conversation with Drake, this time with Aunt Hannah','','inherit','open','open','','350-revision-v1','','','2014-09-10 13:07:37','2014-09-10 20:07:37','',350,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/09/10/350-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(352,1,'2014-08-30 13:09:33','2014-08-30 20:09:33','<em><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">Conversation with Drake, after trying hard to help him win at the matching game (\'Memory,\' you fellow moms!), to puzzling results--Drake turns over many cards, gives me many meaningful looks, but doesn\'t manage to collect any matching pairs himself.</span></em><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you too tired for the matching game, Buddy? It\'s taking us a long time to find matches tonight.</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> UGH. NO, but I\'m just FRUSTRATE</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #37404e;\">D.\r\n<strong>Me <em>(thinking I\'ve offended him because I noticed he was slow on picking up matches)</em>:</strong> Why so frustrated, my friend?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Because I keep TRYING and TRYING to help YOU WIN, but you aren\'t getting ANY of my CLUES!!!\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Oh! Sorry, Buddy. I didn\'t know you wanted me to win.\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>sighing</em>:</strong> It\'s ok, Mom. Just try to pay closer attention, OK?</span>','Drake, playing Memory with Mommy','','publish','open','open','','drake-playing-memory','','','2014-09-10 13:09:51','2014-09-10 20:09:51','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=352',0,'post','',0),(353,1,'2014-09-10 13:09:33','2014-09-10 20:09:33','<em><span style=\"color: #37404e;\">Conversation with Drake, after trying hard to help him win at the matching game (\'Memory,\' you fellow moms!), to puzzling results--Drake turns over many cards, gives me many meaningful looks, but doesn\'t manage to collect any matching pairs himself.</span></em><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you too tired for the matching game, Buddy? It\'s taking us a long time to find matches tonight.</span><br style=\"color: #37404e;\" /><span style=\"color: #37404e;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> UGH. NO, but I\'m just FRUSTRATE</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #37404e;\">D.\r\n<strong>Me <em>(thinking I\'ve offended him 