et/hphotos-ak-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/10615959_10100218516922216_3908948995818706118_n.jpg?oh=67882b172f250ebcd9ed11cd066b34ce&amp;oe=54CCE557&amp;__gda__=1418228545_5cc70c06bcf5b2d9981e913ea4a93296\" alt=\"Drake slurps up his milk\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />','Drake eats cereal like Daddy','','inherit','open','open','','357-revision-v1','','','2014-09-10 13:14:06','2014-09-10 20:14:06','',357,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/09/10/357-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(361,1,'2014-11-12 23:04:27','2014-11-13 07:04:27','<em><strong><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Conversation in the car with Drake</span></strong></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me: </strong>Let\'s go home and read some books!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, <em>sadly</em>: </strong>I like my books. But I have readed them and readed them. I wish I could have new books all the time.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, I know where we need to go...</span>','Drake at the Library','','publish','open','open','','drake-at-the-library','','','2014-11-12 23:04:27','2014-11-13 07:04:27','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=361',0,'post','',0),(362,1,'2014-11-12 23:04:27','2014-11-13 07:04:27','<em><strong><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Conversation in the car with Drake</span></strong></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me: </strong>Let\'s go home and read some books!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, <em>sadly</em>: </strong>I like my books. But I have readed them and readed them. I wish I could have new books all the time.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, I know where we need to go...</span>','Drake at the Library','','inherit','open','open','','361-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:04:27','2014-11-13 07:04:27','',361,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/361-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(363,1,'2014-11-10 23:07:00','2014-11-11 07:07:00','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mom! Mom, I will lay back and you take my picture! From right over me! </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ok. *After a few attempts that Drake wants to re-do, I take the photo in this post*</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> It\'s perfect! I call it \"Resting My Hair In Hot Water.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> It\'s a great work of art, Buddy.</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yeah. It really makes you think.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg\" alt=\"10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Drake the Artist','','publish','open','open','','drake-the-artist','','','2014-11-12 23:20:59','2014-11-13 07:20:59','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=363',0,'post','',0),(364,1,'2014-11-12 23:06:56','2014-11-13 07:06:56','','10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n','','inherit','open','open','','10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n','','','2014-11-12 23:06:56','2014-11-13 07:06:56','',363,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(365,1,'2014-11-12 23:07:00','2014-11-13 07:07:00','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mom! Mom, I will lay back and you take my picture! From right over me! </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ok. *After a few attempts that Drake wants to re-do, I take the photo in this post*</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> It\'s perfect! I call it \"Resting My Hair In Hot Water.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> It\'s a great work of art, Buddy.</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yeah. It really makes you think.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-364\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>','Drake the Artist','','inherit','open','open','','363-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:07:00','2014-11-13 07:07:00','',363,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/363-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(366,1,'2014-11-08 23:08:36','2014-11-09 07:08:36','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">What does a boy do when he parties hard until 10 p.m. with Yammo and P-Pop, then spends the day eating candy, going to the movies, and playing lots of Hotwheels? He finds his \'green wen,\' gets himself cozy in Mom\'s bed, and takes a sneaky nap, of course.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg\" alt=\"10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Sneaky Nap','','publish','open','open','','sneaky-nap','','','2014-11-12 23:21:21','2014-11-13 07:21:21','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=366',0,'post','',0),(367,1,'2014-11-12 23:08:33','2014-11-13 07:08:33','','10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n','','inherit','open','open','','10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n','','','2014-11-12 23:08:33','2014-11-13 07:08:33','',366,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(368,1,'2014-11-12 23:08:36','2014-11-13 07:08:36','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">What does a boy do when he parties hard until 10 p.m. with Yammo and P-Pop, then spends the day eating candy, going to the movies, and playing lots of Hotwheels? He finds his \'green wen,\' gets himself cozy in Mom\'s bed, and takes a sneaky nap, of course.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-367\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a>','Sneaky Nap','','inherit','open','open','','366-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:08:36','2014-11-13 07:08:36','',366,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/366-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(369,1,'2014-11-08 23:09:33','2014-11-09 07:09:33','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ok, Buddy, you can pick a Halloween candy from the bowl.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">*Drake picks a Lemonhead*</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> That\'s a Lemonhead, and it\'s hard candy. You won\'t be able to chew it, you just suck on it.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">*Drake struggles with the candy for several minutes, trying the bite it/chew it with no success.*</span></em><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>with a deep sigh</em>:</strong> Mom, maybe you should have just said \'No\' when I choosed the Lemonhead.</span>','Halloween Candy','','publish','open','open','','halloween-candy','','','2014-11-12 23:09:46','2014-11-13 07:09:46','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=369',0,'post','',0),(370,1,'2014-11-12 23:09:33','2014-11-13 07:09:33','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ok, Buddy, you can pick a Halloween candy from the bowl.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">*Drake picks a Lemonhead*</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> That\'s a Lemonhead, and it\'s hard candy. You won\'t be able to chew it, you just suck on it.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">*Drake struggles with the candy for several minutes, trying the bite it/chew it with no success.*</span></em><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>with a deep sigh</em>:</strong> Mom, maybe you should have just said \'No\' when I choosed the Lemonhead.</span>','Halloween Candy','','inherit','open','open','','369-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:09:33','2014-11-13 07:09:33','',369,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/369-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(371,1,'2014-11-07 23:09:58','2014-11-08 07:09:58','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Hey Drake, tonight you are going to hang out with Yammo Melissa and do something you have NEVER done before!!!\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>super excited</em>:</strong> IS IT CAGE FIGHTING?!?!?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Umm, what?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>(The new activity is miniature golf, people. Not cage fighting.)</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','New Activity','','publish','open','open','','new-activity','','','2014-11-12 23:10:43','2014-11-13 07:10:43','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=371',0,'post','',0),(372,1,'2014-11-12 23:10:29','2014-11-13 07:10:29','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Hey Drake, tonight you are going to hang out with Yammo Melissa and do something you have NEVER done before!!!\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>super excited</em>:</strong> IS IT CAGE FIGHTING?!?!?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Umm, what?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n(The new activity is miniature golf, people. Not cage fighting.)\r\n\r\n</div>','New Activity','','inherit','open','open','','371-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:10:29','2014-11-13 07:10:29','',371,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/371-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(373,1,'2014-11-12 23:10:43','2014-11-13 07:10:43','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Hey Drake, tonight you are going to hang out with Yammo Melissa and do something you have NEVER done before!!!\r\n<strong>Drake, <em>super excited</em>:</strong> IS IT CAGE FIGHTING?!?!?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Umm, what?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>(The new activity is miniature golf, people. Not cage fighting.)</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','New Activity','','inherit','open','open','','371-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:10:43','2014-11-13 07:10:43','',371,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/371-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(374,1,'2014-11-04 23:10:56','2014-11-05 07:10:56','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, I\'m SO tired today. I\'m wiped out.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, <em>lovingly patting my hand</em>:</strong> Oh, Mom, just wait! I\'m going to make you even MORE tired!!</span>','Tired Mommy','','publish','open','open','','tired-mommy','','','2014-11-12 23:11:37','2014-11-13 07:11:37','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=374',0,'post','',0),(375,1,'2014-11-12 23:11:37','2014-11-13 07:11:37','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, I\'m SO tired today. I\'m wiped out.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, <em>lovingly patting my hand</em>:</strong> Oh, Mom, just wait! I\'m going to make you even MORE tired!!</span>','Tired Mommy','','inherit','open','open','','374-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:11:37','2014-11-13 07:11:37','',374,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/374-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(376,1,'2014-10-29 23:12:12','2014-10-30 06:12:12','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too hot. Or maybe it\'s too cold. I don\'t really know.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too yucky.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s poisoned.\" </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too delicious.\"</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\"It\'s too crazy.\" (In that case, he was speaking about plain, buttered noodles.)\r\n\"It\'s too noodly.\" (Again, the noodles.)\r\n\"It\'s too much saucy.\" (About the spaghetti sauce, which I put \"on the side\" at his request.)\r\n\"I might not like it.\"\r\n\"I might like it too much.\"\r\n\"There is a saucy piece on my fork.\"\r\nIn the end, he took one small bite. And, he did not freak out about the presence of something new (raw green bean) on his plate. Generally, he was cheerful at the table. And no gagging! So, progress. Sigh.</span>','A few of the reasons Drake could not try a bite of his dinner','','publish','open','open','','a-few-of-the-reasons-drake-could-not-try-a-bite-of-his-dinner','','','2014-11-12 23:12:34','2014-11-13 07:12:34','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=376',0,'post','',0),(377,1,'2014-11-12 23:12:34','2014-11-13 07:12:34','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too hot. Or maybe it\'s too cold. I don\'t really know.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too yucky.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s poisoned.\" </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"It\'s too delicious.\"</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\"It\'s too crazy.\" (In that case, he was speaking about plain, buttered noodles.)\r\n\"It\'s too noodly.\" (Again, the noodles.)\r\n\"It\'s too much saucy.\" (About the spaghetti sauce, which I put \"on the side\" at his request.)\r\n\"I might not like it.\"\r\n\"I might like it too much.\"\r\n\"There is a saucy piece on my fork.\"\r\nIn the end, he took one small bite. And, he did not freak out about the presence of something new (raw green bean) on his plate. Generally, he was cheerful at the table. And no gagging! So, progress. Sigh.</span>','A few of the reasons Drake could not try a bite of his dinner','','inherit','open','open','','376-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:12:34','2014-11-13 07:12:34','',376,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/376-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(378,1,'2014-10-13 23:13:58','2014-10-14 06:13:58','<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-379 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n.jpg\" alt=\"1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Brownie batter makes Drake do this','','publish','open','open','','brownie-batter-makes-drake-do-this','','','2014-11-12 23:14:13','2014-11-13 07:14:13','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=378',0,'post','',0),(379,1,'2014-11-12 23:13:37','2014-11-13 07:13:37','','1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n','','inherit','open','open','','1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n','','','2014-11-12 23:13:37','2014-11-13 07:13:37','',378,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(380,1,'2014-11-12 23:13:58','2014-11-13 07:13:58','<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-379 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n.jpg\" alt=\"1779779_10100249847899686_1960619393285432961_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Brownie batter makes Drake do this','','inherit','open','open','','378-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:13:58','2014-11-13 07:13:58','',378,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/378-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(381,1,'2014-09-29 23:14:37','2014-09-30 06:14:37','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Hey, red car. You can\'t be bumping the other cars! It\'s not nice and it\'s against our family rules.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">**I perk up and start listening when I hear the phrase I use so often to correct Drake**</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> I love you too much to let you have bad habits, my friend. And I love you too much to let you be unkind when I know you have a kind heart.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">**I\'m feeling like a fantastic parent because he clearly knows why he is sometimes </span></em><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\"><em>corrected. He\'s acting it out with his toys. It\'s adorable.**</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> There are consequences when you do bad things.\r\n<em>**\"Amen,\" I think to myself.**</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> So, next time you bump another car, I\'m going to punch you as hard as I can in your face. Okay, red car Buddy?\r\n<em>**Ummm, what?**</em></span>','Overheard Conversation with Drake and a toy race car','','publish','open','open','','overheard-conversation-with-drake-and-a-toy-race-car','','','2014-11-12 23:15:28','2014-11-13 07:15:28','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=381',0,'post','',0),(382,1,'2014-11-12 23:15:28','2014-11-13 07:15:28','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Hey, red car. You can\'t be bumping the other cars! It\'s not nice and it\'s against our family rules.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">**I perk up and start listening when I hear the phrase I use so often to correct Drake**</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> I love you too much to let you have bad habits, my friend. And I love you too much to let you be unkind when I know you have a kind heart.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">**I\'m feeling like a fantastic parent because he clearly knows why he is sometimes </span></em><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\"><em>corrected. He\'s acting it out with his toys. It\'s adorable.**</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> There are consequences when you do bad things.\r\n<em>**\"Amen,\" I think to myself.**</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> So, next time you bump another car, I\'m going to punch you as hard as I can in your face. Okay, red car Buddy?\r\n<em>**Ummm, what?**</em></span>','Overheard Conversation with Drake and a toy race car','','inherit','open','open','','381-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:15:28','2014-11-13 07:15:28','',381,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/381-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(383,1,'2014-09-27 23:15:42','2014-09-28 06:15:42','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Is it okay, Buddy?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Wow, babe! You are really good at making these cookies!</span>','Conversation with Drake, after he tried one of the cookies I made','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-after-he-tried-one-of-the-cookies-i-made','','','2014-11-12 23:16:07','2014-11-13 07:16:07','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=383',0,'post','',0),(384,1,'2014-11-12 23:16:07','2014-11-13 07:16:07','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Is it okay, Buddy?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Wow, babe! You are really good at making these cookies!</span>','Conversation with Drake, after he tried one of the cookies I made','','inherit','open','open','','383-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:16:07','2014-11-13 07:16:07','',383,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/383-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(387,1,'2014-08-10 23:18:28','2014-08-11 06:18:28','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Is there anything you want to pray about tonight?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yes! I want to tell Jesus that He is good, and I want to tell Him that I can do ALL things through Him because He gives me strength.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> That\'s great, Lovey! Anything you want to ask him?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> No, that\'s ok. God already knows the stuff I need.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>Wise, wise, wise kiddo.</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','Conversation with Drake at bedtime','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-at-bedtime','','','2014-11-12 23:19:07','2014-11-13 07:19:07','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=387',0,'post','',0),(388,1,'2014-11-12 23:19:07','2014-11-13 07:19:07','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Is there anything you want to pray about tonight?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yes! I want to tell Jesus that He is good, and I want to tell Him that I can do ALL things through Him because He gives me strength.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> That\'s great, Lovey! Anything you want to ask him?\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> No, that\'s ok. God already knows the stuff I need.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>Wise, wise, wise kiddo.</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','Conversation with Drake at bedtime','','inherit','open','open','','387-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:19:07','2014-11-13 07:19:07','',387,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/387-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(389,1,'2014-11-12 23:20:59','2014-11-13 07:20:59','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mom! Mom, I will lay back and you take my picture! From right over me! </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ok. *After a few attempts that Drake wants to re-do, I take the photo in this post*</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> It\'s perfect! I call it \"Resting My Hair In Hot Water.\"</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> It\'s a great work of art, Buddy.</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Yeah. It really makes you think.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-364 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n.jpg\" alt=\"10433895_10100262511920886_6523550440625315101_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Drake the Artist','','inherit','open','open','','363-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:20:59','2014-11-13 07:20:59','',363,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/363-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(390,1,'2014-11-12 23:21:21','2014-11-13 07:21:21','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">What does a boy do when he parties hard until 10 p.m. with Yammo and P-Pop, then spends the day eating candy, going to the movies, and playing lots of Hotwheels? He finds his \'green wen,\' gets himself cozy in Mom\'s bed, and takes a sneaky nap, of course.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367 size-full\" src=\"http://conversationswithdrake.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n.jpg\" alt=\"10685586_10100261600841696_3316967265168069365_n\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></a>','Sneaky Nap','','inherit','open','open','','366-revision-v1','','','2014-11-12 23:21:21','2014-11-13 07:21:21','',366,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2014/11/12/366-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(392,1,'2015-03-11 22:02:57','2015-03-12 05:02:57','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me, when I heard him slipping into playing with his toy cars instead of picking up:</strong> Hey, my love, are you cleaning or playing?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, with a sheepish smile:</strong> Ummmmm, I\'m multitasking?</span>','Conversation with Drake, while we tidied up his room','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-while-we-tidied-up-his-room','','','2015-03-11 22:02:57','2015-03-12 05:02:57','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=392',0,'post','',0),(393,1,'2015-03-11 22:02:57','2015-03-12 05:02:57','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me, when I heard him slipping into playing with his toy cars instead of picking up:</strong> Hey, my love, are you cleaning or playing?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, with a sheepish smile:</strong> Ummmmm, I\'m multitasking?</span>','Conversation with Drake, while we tidied up his room','','inherit','open','open','','392-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:02:57','2015-03-12 05:02:57','',392,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/392-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(394,1,'2015-03-11 22:04:06','2015-03-12 05:04:06','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Okay, Buddy, I\'m going to my class! Have fun with Daddy! I\'ll come kiss you goodnight when I get back.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Okay Mom!\r\n</span><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">glances at </span><a class=\"profileLink\" style=\"color: #3b5998;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/adrianjonmiller\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/user.php?id=134900256\">Adrian</a></em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">.\r\n</span><strong>Drake:</strong> Ummm, I\'m in charge while you\'re gone, right?','Drake in charge','','publish','open','open','','drake-in-charge','','','2015-03-11 22:04:06','2015-03-12 05:04:06','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=394',0,'post','',0),(395,1,'2015-03-11 22:04:06','2015-03-12 05:04:06','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Okay, Buddy, I\'m going to my class! Have fun with Daddy! I\'ll come kiss you goodnight when I get back.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Okay Mom!\r\n</span><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">glances at </span><a class=\"profileLink\" style=\"color: #3b5998;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/adrianjonmiller\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/user.php?id=134900256\">Adrian</a></em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">.\r\n</span><strong>Drake:</strong> Ummm, I\'m in charge while you\'re gone, right?','Drake in charge','','inherit','open','open','','394-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:04:06','2015-03-12 05:04:06','',394,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/394-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(396,1,'2015-03-11 22:04:07','2015-03-12 05:04:07','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me, when I heard him slipping into playing with his toy cars instead of picking up:</strong> Hey, my love, are you cleaning or playing?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, with a sheepish smile:</strong> Ummmmm, I\'m multitasking?</span>','Conversation with Drake, while we tidied up his room','','inherit','open','open','','392-autosave-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:04:07','2015-03-12 05:04:07','',392,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/392-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(397,1,'2015-03-03 22:05:12','2015-03-04 06:05:12','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, while he gives me a big hug:</strong> Mom, you\'re sooooo beautiful and soooo cute today.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Thanks, Buddy!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Did you do something different with your hairs?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> I don\'t think so.<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Well they look really good.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Thanks!\r\n<em>****long, awkward pause****</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> So....I need to ask you for something.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>(It was a new racetrack. The kid\'s got game.)</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','Drake\'s got game','','publish','open','open','','drakes-got-game','','','2015-03-11 22:06:29','2015-03-12 05:06:29','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=397',0,'post','',0),(398,1,'2015-03-11 22:06:29','2015-03-12 05:06:29','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, while he gives me a big hug:</strong> Mom, you\'re sooooo beautiful and soooo cute today.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Thanks, Buddy!\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Did you do something different with your hairs?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> I don\'t think so.<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Well they look really good.\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Thanks!\r\n<em>****long, awkward pause****</em>\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> So....I need to ask you for something.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">\r\n\r\n<em>(It was a new racetrack. The kid\'s got game.)</em>\r\n\r\n</div>','Drake\'s got game','','inherit','open','open','','397-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:06:29','2015-03-12 05:06:29','',397,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/397-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(399,1,'2015-02-25 22:06:33','2015-02-26 06:06:33','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"No bumping, no pushing, no pooping, no throwing socks, no pinching. Violations of the rules get a time out pit stop.\"</span>','Drake\'s rules of racing, as explained to his Hotwheels this morning','','publish','open','open','','drakes-rules-of-racing-as-explained-to-his-hotwheels-this-morning','','','2015-03-11 22:07:03','2015-03-12 05:07:03','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=399',0,'post','',0),(400,1,'2015-03-11 22:07:03','2015-03-12 05:07:03','<span style=\"color: #141823;\">\"No bumping, no pushing, no pooping, no throwing socks, no pinching. Violations of the rules get a time out pit stop.\"</span>','Drake\'s rules of racing, as explained to his Hotwheels this morning','','inherit','open','open','','399-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:07:03','2015-03-12 05:07:03','',399,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/399-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(401,1,'2015-02-23 22:07:32','2015-02-24 06:07:32','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Cap:</strong> let\'s take a picture with super hero poses!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> okay! You be Captain America! I\'ll be HULK!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Cap strikes a pose with his shield, Drake throws down his best Hulk SMASH, and I take my favorite photo in the history of the world\r\n<img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://fbcdn-sphotos-g-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfp1/v/t1.0-9/10998319_10100318295704736_2983692936066117812_n.jpg?oh=34b5f8a0c6088137d3ee657ba176ab6b&amp;oe=5580F331&amp;__gda__=1435260500_dea8b609ea2a89d4bec6e68249f51a5b\" alt=\"Drake and Captain America\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n</span></em>','Conversation with Drake AND CAPTAIN AMERICA:','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-and-captain-america','','','2015-03-11 22:09:31','2015-03-12 05:09:31','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=401',0,'post','',0),(402,1,'2015-03-11 22:09:31','2015-03-12 05:09:31','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Cap:</strong> let\'s take a picture with super hero poses!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> okay! You be Captain America! I\'ll be HULK!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Cap strikes a pose with his shield, Drake throws down his best Hulk SMASH, and I take my favorite photo in the history of the world\r\n<img class=\"alignleft\" src=\"https://fbcdn-sphotos-g-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfp1/v/t1.0-9/10998319_10100318295704736_2983692936066117812_n.jpg?oh=34b5f8a0c6088137d3ee657ba176ab6b&amp;oe=5580F331&amp;__gda__=1435260500_dea8b609ea2a89d4bec6e68249f51a5b\" alt=\"Drake and Captain America\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" />\r\n</span></em>','Conversation with Drake AND CAPTAIN AMERICA:','','inherit','open','open','','401-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:09:31','2015-03-12 05:09:31','',401,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/401-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(403,1,'2015-02-14 22:10:17','2015-02-15 06:10:17','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Daddy:</strong> You and Yammo Melissa should play tip tap toe tonight (Drake\'s name for tic tac toe).</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, in a superior tone:</strong> I\'m very good at it. </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Yammo:</strong> And humble.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> No. I\'m not good at humble.</span>','Conversation with Drake, and Daddy and Yammo Melissa','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-and-daddy-and-yammo-melissa','','','2015-03-11 22:11:06','2015-03-12 05:11:06','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=403',0,'post','',0),(404,1,'2015-03-11 22:11:06','2015-03-12 05:11:06','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Daddy:</strong> You and Yammo Melissa should play tip tap toe tonight (Drake\'s name for tic tac toe).</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake, in a superior tone:</strong> I\'m very good at it. </span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Yammo:</strong> And humble.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> No. I\'m not good at humble.</span>','Conversation with Drake, and Daddy and Yammo Melissa','','inherit','open','open','','403-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:11:06','2015-03-12 05:11:06','',403,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/403-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(405,1,'2015-02-05 22:11:32','2015-02-06 06:11:32','<em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Drake enters the room as I select a show on Netflix</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, I want to build all my big tracks in the living room! Don\'t turn on a show, it will distract me so much!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me</strong>: What if I pick something really boring that you won\'t want to watch?\r\n</span><em>I turn on the old BBC Pride and Prejudice mini series</em>\r\n<strong>|Drake:</strong> Perfect! I hate this! I won\'t want to watch it at all!','Drake and Netflix','','publish','open','open','','drake-and-netflix','','','2015-03-11 22:12:35','2015-03-12 05:12:35','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=405',0,'post','',0),(406,1,'2015-03-11 22:12:35','2015-03-12 05:12:35','<em><span style=\"color: #141823;\">Drake enters the room as I select a show on Netflix</span></em><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, I want to build all my big tracks in the living room! Don\'t turn on a show, it will distract me so much!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me</strong>: What if I pick something really boring that you won\'t want to watch?\r\n</span><em>I turn on the old BBC Pride and Prejudice mini series</em>\r\n<strong>|Drake:</strong> Perfect! I hate this! I won\'t want to watch it at all!','Drake and Netflix','','inherit','open','open','','405-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:12:35','2015-03-12 05:12:35','',405,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/405-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(407,1,'2015-02-03 22:12:50','2015-02-04 06:12:50','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, what if you die before I\'m big?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> I\'m not planning on dying before you\'re big, honey. You don\'t need to be worried.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> But if you do, who will make my dinners just how I like and do all the things just how I like?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> What about Daddy? Can\'t Daddy do those things?<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<strong>Drake, rolling his eyes:</strong> Mom. Have you even met Daddy?\r\n</span><em>He really loves his Daddy. Not so confident in his dinner making abilities, though.</em></p>','Drake asks about death','','publish','open','open','','drake-asks-about-death','','','2015-03-11 22:13:43','2015-03-12 05:13:43','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=407',0,'post','',0),(408,1,'2015-03-11 22:13:43','2015-03-12 05:13:43','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, what if you die before I\'m big?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> I\'m not planning on dying before you\'re big, honey. You don\'t need to be worried.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> But if you do, who will make my dinners just how I like and do all the things just how I like?\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> What about Daddy? Can\'t Daddy do those things?<span class=\"text_exposed_show\">\r\n<strong>Drake, rolling his eyes:</strong> Mom. Have you even met Daddy?\r\n</span><em>He really loves his Daddy. Not so confident in his dinner making abilities, though.</em></p>','Drake asks about death','','inherit','open','open','','407-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:13:43','2015-03-12 05:13:43','',407,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/407-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(409,1,'2015-01-16 22:14:22','2015-01-17 06:14:22','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><em>Henry (6 months old) sees Drake\'s dirty bare feet and immediately starts trying to chew them</em>\r\n<strong>Hannah:</strong> *gasps in horror at the germs going into her baby\'s mouth*\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> RELAX, Nana Hookum! It\'s not like he has any teeth or anything!\r\n<em>Oh, Drake. Always looking out for number one.</em></p>','Drake and Henry','','publish','open','open','','drake-and-henry','','','2015-03-11 22:15:16','2015-03-12 05:15:16','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=409',0,'post','',0),(410,1,'2015-03-11 22:15:16','2015-03-12 05:15:16','<p style=\"color: #141823;\"><em>Henry (6 months old) sees Drake\'s dirty bare feet and immediately starts trying to chew them</em>\r\n<strong>Hannah:</strong> *gasps in horror at the germs going into her baby\'s mouth*\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> RELAX, Nana Hookum! It\'s not like he has any teeth or anything!\r\n<em>Oh, Drake. Always looking out for number one.</em></p>','Drake and Henry','','inherit','open','open','','409-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:15:16','2015-03-12 05:15:16','',409,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/409-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(411,1,'2015-01-14 22:16:05','2015-01-15 06:16:05','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, I feel worried about dying.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Why are you worried, sweet guy?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> What if Jesus decides it\'s my time and he pokes a hole in me and I die? What if it hurts? What if I\'m not Drake any more when I\'m in heaven? What if you aren\'t my mommy anymore?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Wow, Drake. Some of those questions are big questions. But I know that you will ALWAYS be Drake--God made you to be just like you are. And I\'ll always love you! And Jesus doesn\'</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">t poke holes in people, Honey. He will only take you home to Heaven when it\'s the right thing to do.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Okay. Okay. As long as nobody is poking any holes in me.</span>','Conversation with a very sad Drake','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-a-very-sad-drake','','','2015-03-11 22:16:17','2015-03-12 05:16:17','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=411',0,'post','',0),(412,1,'2015-03-11 22:16:05','2015-03-12 05:16:05','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Mommy, I feel worried about dying.</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Why are you worried, sweet guy?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> What if Jesus decides it\'s my time and he pokes a hole in me and I die? What if it hurts? What if I\'m not Drake any more when I\'m in heaven? What if you aren\'t my mommy anymore?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Wow, Drake. Some of those questions are big questions. But I know that you will ALWAYS be Drake--God made you to be just like you are. And I\'ll always love you! And Jesus doesn\'</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\">t poke holes in people, Honey. He will only take you home to Heaven when it\'s the right thing to do.\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> Okay. Okay. As long as nobody is poking any holes in me.</span>','Conversation with a very sad Drake','','inherit','open','open','','411-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:16:05','2015-03-12 05:16:05','',411,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/411-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(413,1,'2015-01-13 22:16:40','2015-01-14 06:16:40','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> oh, look Drake! The dogs are happy to see you. (They run up to the car and wait by Drake\'s door while he climbs out.)</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake</strong>,<em> genuinely relieved</em>: My dogs! My dogs! You\'re ALIVE!!!!</span>','Conversation with Drake, as we pulled into the driveway at home','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-as-we-pulled-into-the-driveway-at-home','','','2015-03-11 22:17:14','2015-03-12 05:17:14','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=413',0,'post','',0),(414,1,'2015-03-11 22:17:14','2015-03-12 05:17:14','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> oh, look Drake! The dogs are happy to see you. (They run up to the car and wait by Drake\'s door while he climbs out.)</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake</strong>,<em> genuinely relieved</em>: My dogs! My dogs! You\'re ALIVE!!!!</span>','Conversation with Drake, as we pulled into the driveway at home','','inherit','open','open','','413-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:17:14','2015-03-12 05:17:14','',413,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/413-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(415,1,'2015-01-02 22:17:43','2015-01-03 06:17:43','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> \"I don\'t really knoooow where I came from. Mommy says I grew in her tummy, but I know that\'s not the whooooole stoooorrrrry.\"</span>','Overheard song by Drake, as he played in his room','','publish','open','open','','overheard-song-by-drake-as-he-played-in-his-room','','','2015-03-11 22:18:01','2015-03-12 05:18:01','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=415',0,'post','',0),(416,1,'2015-03-11 22:18:01','2015-03-12 05:18:01','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> \"I don\'t really knoooow where I came from. Mommy says I grew in her tummy, but I know that\'s not the whooooole stoooorrrrry.\"</span>','Overheard song by Drake, as he played in his room','','inherit','open','open','','415-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:18:01','2015-03-12 05:18:01','',415,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/415-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(417,1,'2015-01-02 22:18:49','2015-01-03 06:18:49','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, let\'s make a cake!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> yeah! With swirls and sprinkles and Legos you can eat and gold dust and tiny strawberries and Captain America standing on the top like he is WINNING!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ummm, how about chocolate instead?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Ok! Aunt </span><a class=\"profileLink\" style=\"color: #3b5998;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dena.doyle\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/user.php?id=3230826\">Dena</a><span style=\"color: #141823;\"> can make me the other one.</span>','Drake wants to make cake','','publish','open','open','','drake-wants-to-make-cake','','','2015-03-11 22:19:33','2015-03-12 05:19:33','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=417',0,'post','',0),(418,1,'2015-03-11 22:19:33','2015-03-12 05:19:33','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, let\'s make a cake!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> yeah! With swirls and sprinkles and Legos you can eat and gold dust and tiny strawberries and Captain America standing on the top like he is WINNING!</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Ummm, how about chocolate instead?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> Ok! Aunt </span><a class=\"profileLink\" style=\"color: #3b5998;\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dena.doyle\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/user.php?id=3230826\">Dena</a><span style=\"color: #141823;\"> can make me the other one.</span>','Drake wants to make cake','','inherit','open','open','','417-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:19:33','2015-03-12 05:19:33','',417,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/417-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(419,1,'2014-12-16 22:19:58','2014-12-17 06:19:58','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake: </strong>How come we were so mean to Japan?\r\n</span><em>The documentary was discussing confiscation of family samurai swords</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Because we just had a war with Japan, and we were angry and afraid that Japan might hurt us again.\\\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> I\'m glad we don\'t have wars anymore.\r\n<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Oh, sweet boy. We live in a place that is very safe from war, but right now, there are many wars in other parts of</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\"> the world.\r\n</span><strong>Drake,</strong><em> tears in his eyes</em><strong>:</strong> Tell those guys to stop it, Mom. They should do a lot of timeouts.','Conversation with Drake, while watching a documentary about American occupation of Japan after WWII','','publish','open','open','','conversation-with-drake-while-watching-a-documentary-about-american-occupation-of-japan-after-wwii','','','2015-03-11 22:21:30','2015-03-12 05:21:30','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=419',0,'post','',0),(420,1,'2015-03-11 22:21:30','2015-03-12 05:21:30','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake: </strong>How come we were so mean to Japan?\r\n</span><em>The documentary was discussing confiscation of family samurai swords</em>\r\n<strong>Me:</strong> Because we just had a war with Japan, and we were angry and afraid that Japan might hurt us again.\\\r\n<strong>Drake:</strong> I\'m glad we don\'t have wars anymore.\r\n<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Oh, sweet boy. We live in a place that is very safe from war, but right now, there are many wars in other parts of</span><span class=\"text_exposed_show\" style=\"color: #141823;\"> the world.\r\n</span><strong>Drake,</strong><em> tears in his eyes</em><strong>:</strong> Tell those guys to stop it, Mom. They should do a lot of timeouts.','Conversation with Drake, while watching a documentary about American occupation of Japan after WWII','','inherit','open','open','','419-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:21:30','2015-03-12 05:21:30','',419,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/419-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(421,1,'2014-12-10 22:21:44','2014-12-11 06:21:44','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you a pessimist or an optimist?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> OPTIMUS PRIME!!!!</span>','Drakes class is always...','','publish','open','open','','drakes-class-is-always','','','2015-03-11 22:22:16','2015-03-12 05:22:16','',0,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/?p=421',0,'post','',0),(422,1,'2015-03-11 22:22:16','2015-03-12 05:22:16','<span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Me:</strong> Drake, are you a pessimist or an optimist?</span><br style=\"color: #141823;\" /><span style=\"color: #141823;\"><strong>Drake:</strong> OPTIMUS PRIME!!!!</span>','Drakes class is always...','','inherit','open','open','','421-revision-v1','','','2015-03-11 22:22:16','2015-03-12 05:22:16','',421,'http://conversationswithdrake.com/2015/03/11/421-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
